ğŸ“Š Dataset Key Features
The analysis utilizes the following attributes:
User & Session IDs: Unique identifiers for tracking individual journeys.
Event Types: User actions (Browse, Add to Cart, Checkout, Purchase).
Timestamp: Precise time of action for trend analysis.
Attributes: Device, Region, and Marketing Channel.
Outcome Metrics: Revenue generated and Bounce Flag status.

